{
  "stem": "11957.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when you do it over and over again, you get used to it like anything else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not-- not for the sake of shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I shoot-- I shot some people in a battle, in a war, like the Banderovcis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they surrounded us, and they wanted to chase us out of that area where we were-- where we were stationed, we had our camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had only about 200 people at one time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They surrounded us with 600 people strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were fighting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we made our way out of that--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That area.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to a different area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called Turemne, Turemne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "T-U-R-E-M-N-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Turemne.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a woods where they had-- we had water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a water spout coming there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had water there, and we kept our camp there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we had another camp for the winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had pine trees in that camp for the winter because you could-- with an airplane you could see, you know, the Germans used to fly over that area.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they see something going on there, they used to throw bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we-- in the wintertime, we had to go to different camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'42 and '43.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you're busy trying to inflict as much damage--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trying to survive and-- and do the most damage we-- we could do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they would say here--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would say here is a good spot where to blow up the train because it was a curving area, where the-- where the train had to curve.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's usually a good area because when you blow it up, it comes-- pulls all the rest of the--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cars with it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If it was ammunition there, we took the ammunition with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes there were troops.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
